  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Eyes on the Landing Beach Committees</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Community sensitisation outreach on corrupt practices in the fisheries sector
Capacity Building workshops for fishermen, fishmongers and volunteers on strategies to curb corruption in the fishing industry.
Build or utilise existing but common electronic platforms where volunteers could anonymously share information on smuggled fuel to duty bearers especially the security agencies.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Create a model system where premix allocations are made to fishermen in a more transparent, equitable and inclusive manner.</narrative>
  </description>
